 <section xml:id="troubleshooting-el8-quickstart">
  <title>Troubleshooting</title>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>nginx.service not running after installing RMT</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Not sure yet, need to investigate
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Liberty product doesn't appear after rmt-cli sync</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Check your network. If network is down the sync command won't throw an error, but it also won't sync anything.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Zypper error</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Check if libzypp version 16.20.4 or higher is installed.
     </para>
     <remark>Might not need this anymore as the original note is two years old and current libzypp is version 17+</remark>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </section>
